Fplayers%2F107509-prasidh-krishna-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPrasidh%20Krishna%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20pasting%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20not%20a%20400-run%20wicket%20and%20we%20gave%20too%20many%20runs.%20We%20sprayed%20the%20ball%20all%20around%2C%20but%20it%20happens.%20One%20can't%20depend%20on%20one%20particular%20bowler%20(Bumrah)%2C%20the%20other%20three%20pacers%20also%20needed%20to%20perform%20their%20roles%2C%20we%20could%20learn%20from%20how%20South%20Africa%20bowled%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20admitted%20that%20although%20there%20wasn't%20lack%20of%20effort%20but%20Bumrah%20couldn't%20alone%20keep%20the%20pressure%20on%20Proteas%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBumrah%20bowled%20well%20and%20we%20all%20know%20his%20quality.%20All%20he%20wanted%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20support%20which%20he%20didn't%20get.%20That%20happens.%20All%20three%20tried%20hard%2C%20bending%20their%20backs%20but%20didn't%20happen%20the%20way%20we%20wanted%20to.%20But%20games%20like%20these%20teaches%20you%20a%20lot%20as%20to%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%20as%20a%20bowling%20unit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20skipper%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20Prasidh%2C%20who%20has%20just%20had%2012%20first-class%20matches%20under%20his%20belt%2C%20couldn't%20get%20the%20measure%20of%20bounce%20and%20carry%20at%20Supersport%20Park%20and%20went%20for%2093%20runs%20in%2020%20overs%20on%20Test%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skipper%20conceded%20Prasidh%20is%20a%20bit%20under-cooked%20but%20also%20insisted%20that%20his%20team%20would%20show%20faith%20in%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20he%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20inexperienced.%20He%20has%20got%20the%20tools%20to%20come%20out%20here%20and%20play%20the%20game.%20Obviously%2C%20if%20I%20look%20at%20the%20bowlers%20that%20we%20have%20back%20in%20India%2C%20some%20of%20them%20are%20injured%2C%20some%20not%20available%2C%20so%20we%20tried%20pickin