.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20is%20%26quot%3Bengaged%20with%20industry%20on%20a%20near-daily%20basis%20to%20gauge%20needs%20and%20provide%20reassurance%20that%20the%20international%20community%20is%20there%20to%20help%20with%20safe%20passage%2C%26quot%3B%20Air%20Force%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Bryon%20McGarry%2C%20a%20Defense%20Department%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Africa%2C%20said%20Thursday%20in%20an%20emailed%20response%20to%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20that's%20not%20proving%20enough%20for%20most%20shipping%20lines%20to%20gamble%20that%20a%20drone%20or%20missile%20aimed%20at%20their%20vessels%20won't%20be%20one%20that%20gets%20past%20the%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20take%20a%20little%20while%20for%20shippers%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20about%20the%20security%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20retired%20Marine%20officer%20and%20senior%20adviser%20with%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20in%20Washington.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20the%20US%20and%20the%20coalition%20can%20maintain%20safe%20passage%2C%20then%20I%20think%20they'll%20come%20back.%20But%20right%20now%20they%20really%20can't%20be%20sure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECancian%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20some%20shippers%20will%20remain%20%26quot%3Bmore%20risk-averse%20than%20others.%20Ones%20that%20have%20connections%20with%20Israel%20might%20be%20more%20reticent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%2C%20who%20are%20backed%20by%20Iran%2C%20have%20said%20they're%20targeting%20ships%20linked%20to%20Israel%20to%20show%20support%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20though%20ships%20without%20direct%20links%20to%20Israel%20also%20have%20been%20singled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalf%20of%20the%20container-ship%20fleet%20that%20regularly%20transits%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Suez%20Canal%20is%20avoiding%20the%20route%20now%20because%20of%20the%20threat%20of%20attacks%2C%20according%20to%20new%20industry%20data.%20Many%20tankers%20and%20container%20ships%20are%20resorting%20to%20the%20longer%20-%20and%20costlier%20-%20route%20around%20the%20southern%20tip%20of%20Africa%2C%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20higher%20prices%20for%20oil%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20consumer%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA.P.%20Moller-Maersk%20A%2FS%2C%20the%20world's%20No.%202%20container%20line%2C%20said%20it's%20preparing%20to%20resume%20Red%20Sea%20passages%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20operationally%20possible.%26quot%3B%20But%20even%20Maersk%20has%20cautioned%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20overall%20risk%20is%20not%20eliminated%20in%20the%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20company%20said%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bnot%20hesitate%26quot%3B%20to%20re-evaluate%20the%20safety%20situation%20for%20its%20vessels%20and%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGene%20Moran%2C%20a%20defense%20analyst%20and%20retired%20Navy%20captain%2C%20once%20commanded%20the%20USS%20Laboon%2C%20the%20destroyer%20that%20shot%20down%20four%20drones%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20Saturday.%20From%20his%20perspective%2C%20the%20shipping%20companies%20are%20still%20looking%20for%20the%20American-led%20coalition%20to%20do%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20method%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20address%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20Moran%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Houthis%20are%20able%20to%20operate%20from%20the%20uncontrolled%20portions%20of%20Yemen.%20Something%20will%20need%20to%20be%20done%20about%20that.%20We%20seem%20to%20be%20moving%20very%20gingerly%20when%20the%20conditions%20seem%20to%20call%20for%20a%20more%20forceful%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20been%20reluctant%20to%20take%20action%20that%20could%20turn%20Israel's%20war%20against%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20-%20which%20began%20after%20that%20group's%20Oct.%207%20assault%20on%20Israel%20-%20into%20a%20broader%20regional%20conflict.%20Shipping%20companies%20may%20share%20that%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20United%20States%20were%20to%20start%20shooting%20at%20Houthi%20camps%2C%20that%20would%20arguably%20increase%20the%20risk%2C%20not%20decrease%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Cancian%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20shippers%20are%20particularly%20anxious%20to%20start%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20Traffic%20Through%20the%20Suez%20Canal%20%7C%20The%20daily%20number%20of%20tanker%20and%20cargo%20ship%20crossings%20has%20slipped%20this%20month%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20has%20said%20the%20Red%20Sea%20security%20initiative%20it's%20leading%20-%20named%20Operation%20Prosperity%20Guardian%20-%20brings%20together%20forces%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20Canada%2C%20France%2C%20Italy%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20Norway%2C%20the%20Seychelles%2C%20Spain%2C%20Australia%20and%20Greece%20as%20well%20as%20some%20other%20nations%20that%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20named.%20Yet%20the%20military%20hasn't%20spelled%20out%20details%20of%20how%20it%20will%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20General%20Pat%20Ryder%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20press%20secretary%2C%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20the%20coalition%20will%20function%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhighway%20patrol%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoran%20said%20that%20the%20mixed%20nature%20of%20the%20threat%2C%20which%20includes%20potential%20attacks%20from%20drones%2C%20missiles%20and%20small%20boats%2C%20makes%20it%20more%20challenging%20to%20respond%20because%20not%20all%20the%20ships%20participating%20in%20the%20force%20will%20have%20the%20same%20capabilities%20as%20the%20US%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20operation%20will%20continue%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20putting%20a%20timeline%20on%20this%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20McGarry%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20spokesperson.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20stand%20firm%20with%20our%20partners%20in%20the%20