2%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225349%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Open%20female%20mouth%20during%20oral%20checkup%20at%20the%20dentist.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658e1bbb1c5c7b8c9a0cbc87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Minnesota%20woman%20sued%20her%20dentist%20who%20performed%20an%20operation%20that%20included%20four%20root%20canals%2C%20eight%20dental%20crowns%2C%20and%2020%20fillings%20in%20one%20sitting.%3Cp%3EBojan89%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKathleen%20Wilson%20underwent%20an%20extensive%20dental%20operation%20in%202020%20that%20she%20says%20disfigured%20her.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20dentist%20attempted%20to%20address%20decay%20that%20was%20spreading%20in%20her%20mouth%20in%20one%20visit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20operation%20lasted%205.5%20hours%2C%20and%20Wilson%20was%20given%20almost%20twice%20the%20max%20dosage%20of%20anesthesia%2C%20an%20expert%20wrote.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Minnesota%20woman%20has%20sued%20her%20dentist%20after%20receiving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-you-should-go-to-the-dentist-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efour%20root%20canals%2C%20eight%20dental%20crowns%2C%20and%2020%20fillings%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20single%20visit%20that%20she%20says%20led%20to%20her%20disfigurement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Wilson%20filed%20the%20lawsuit%20last%20week%20in%20Hennepin%20County%20District%20Court%2C%20accusing%20Dr.%20Kevin%20Molldrem%20of%20Molldrem%20Family%20Dentistry%20in%20Eden%20Prairie%2C%20Minnesota%2C%20of%20providing%20negligent%20treatment%20in%20July%202020%20that%20caused%20significant%20injuries%20to%20Wilson%2C%20along%20with%20providing%20an%20unsafe%20dosage%20of%20anesthesia%20and%20falsifying%20medical%20records%20to%20cover%20it%20up%2C%20according%20to%20court%20documents.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolldrem%20and%20his%20attorney%2C%20Nathaniel%20Weimer%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20The%20Associated%20Press%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.startribune.com%2Fpatient-sues-eden-prairie-dentist-for-visit-included-eight-crowns-four-root-canals-and-20-fillings%2F600330583%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Star%20Tribune%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20first%20reported%20on%20the%20case%2C%20Wilson's%20legal%20team%20retained%20Dr.%20Avrum%20Goldstein%2C%20a%20dentist%20in%20Florida%2C%20to%20provide%20an%20expert%20opinion%20and%20review%20Wilson's%20medical%20records%20from%20Molldrem%20and%20subsequent%20providers.%20Goldstein's%20Nov.%2014%20report%20identified%20various%20duty-of-care%20breaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldstein%20said%20in%20the%20report%20that%20Molldrem%20made%20the%20right%20diagnosis%2C%20but%20he%20provided%20poor-quality%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDr.%20Molldrem%20was%20confronted%20with%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20not%20only%20had%20extensive%20decay%2C%20but%20erosion%20and%20dissolution%20of%20her%20teeth%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldstein%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20issues%20were%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20Wilson%20had%20a%20candy-eating%20habit%20and%20irritable%20bowel%20syndrome%2C%20vomiting%20one%20to%20two%20times%20a%20week%2C%20which%20can%20damage%20the%20teeth's%20enamel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20had%20decay%20on%20%26quot%3Bvirtually%20every%20tooth%20in%20her%20mouth%2C%20something%20that%20is%20quite%20rare%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldestein%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolldrem's%20attempt%20to%20restore%20all%20Wilson's%20teeth%20in%20one%20visit%20did%20nothing%20to%20address%20her%20susceptibility%20to%20disease%20or%20the%20potential%20of%20losing%20teeth%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKatie%20required%20a%20slow%2C%20thoughtful%2C%20careful%20and%20measured%20response%20to%20her%20disease.%20Trying%20to%20fill%20every%20hole%20in%20every%20tooth%20in%20her%20mouth%20in%20one%20visit%20is%20not%20only%20the%20antithesis%20of%20what%20was%20indicated%2C%20it%20is%20not%20humanely%20possible%20to%20achieve%20in%20an%20effective%20or%20constructive%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldstein%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Binconceivable%26quot%3B%20to%20address%2028%20teeth%20in%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E5%20%C2%BD%20hours.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20challenge%20of%20a%20long%20appointment%20is%20maintaining%20adequate%20anesthesia%2C%20Goldstein%20said.%20The%20maximum%20dosage%20is%20490%20mg%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Molldrem%20administered%20960%20mg%20to%20Wilson%2C%20he%20wrote.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson's%20records%20show%20that%20Molldrem%20said%20he%20administered%20eight%20tubes%20of%20dental%20anesthetic%2C%20known%20as%20carpules.%20But%20Goldstein%20found%20the%20first%20dose%20alone%20was%20eight%20carpules%2C%20and%20he%20administered%2015%20carpules%20throughout%20the%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20went%20to%20a%20different%20dental%20office%20for%20an%20evaluation%20showing%20recurrent%20decay%20and%20other%20damage.%20For%20several%20months%20in%202022%20she%20was%20treated%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota%20Dental%20School%20%26quot%3Bfor%20repair%20and%20replacement%20of%20many%20of%20her%20restorations%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20stabilize%20her%20mouth%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20of%20Wilson's%20teeth%20end%20up%20having%20to%20be%20removed%20and%20replaced%20with%20implants%2C%20Goldstein%20said%20%26quot%3Ball%20of%20the%20work%20that%20was%20done%20and%20all%20of%20the%20expense%20associated%20with%20it%20will%20have%20been%20for%20nothing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20medical%20costs%2C%20Wilson%20said%20she%20suffered%20pain%2C%20embarrassment%2C%20disfigurement%2C%20and%20distress.%20She%20is%20asking%20for%20at%20least%20%2450%2C000%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20website%2C%20