rs%20for%20her%20role%20in%20the%20death%20of%20her%20mother%20Dee%20Dee%20Blanchard%2C%20who%20prosecutors%20also%20acknowledged%20was%20abusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20picked%20Blanchard%20up%20in%20a%20silver%20Cadillac%2C%20according%20to%20a%20photo%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fgypsy-rose-blanchard-picked-up-prison-release-by-new-husband-wrestling-fan-hitman-hart-license-plate-8420585%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20vanity%20plates%20on%20the%20car%20said%20%26quot%3BHITMAN%2C%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20coincidence%20or%20not%2C%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20events%20that%20put%20Blanchard%20behind%20bars%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWho%20is%20Gypsy%20Rose's%20husband%2C%20Ryan%20Scott%20Anderson%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fwho-is-ryan-scott-anderson-gypsy-rose-blanchard-husband-8420408%3Futm_campaign%3Dpeoplemagazine%26utm_content%3Dnew%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter.com%26utm_term%3D658de2c251a48f0001c2b3d6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Anderson%20is%20a%20middle%20school%20special%20education%20teacher%20from%20Saint%20Charles%2C%20Louisiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20were%20married%20in%20August%202022%20in%20Chillicothe%2C%20Missouri%20while%20Blanchard%20was%20still%20in%20prison%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Springfield%20News-Leader.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%2030%20years%20old%20and%20Anderson%20was%2036%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20wrestling%20fan.%20The%20vanity%20plate%20on%20the%20car%20Anderson%20picked%20Blanchard%20up%20in%20was%20styled%20after%20WWE%20Hall-of-Famer%20Bret%20Hart%2C%20who%20often%20went%20by%20the%20stage%20name%20%26quot%3BThe%20Hitman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlachard%20told%20People%20in%20an%20interview%20before%20her%20release%20that%20Anderson%20was%20a%20crucial%20source%20of%20sup