0other%20Republican%20lawmakers%20have%20suggested%2C%20New%20York%20is%20not%20forcing%20Chick-fil-A%20to%20open%20on%20Sundays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20Chick-fil-A%20closes%20on%20Sundays%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-has-slowest-friendliest-drive-thrus-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChick-fil-A%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20practice%20of%20closing%20on%20Sundays%20was%20started%20by%20its%20late%20founder%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-closed-on-sunday-business-strategy-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES.%20Truett%20Cathy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20has%20continued%20to%20today.%20%26quot%3BClosing%20our%20business%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Lord's%20Day%2C%20is%20our%20way%20of%20honoring%20God%20and%20showing%20our%20loyalty%20to%20Him%2C%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcathy-family-chick-fil-a-fortune-net-worth-lifestyle-photos-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Cathy%2C%20who%20died%20in%202014%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wrote%20in%20his%202002%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20being%20closed.%20It's%20about%20how%20we%20use%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Chick-fil-A%20says%20on%20its%20website.%20%26quot%3BSo%20while%20we're%20off%20today%2C%20we%20hope%20you%20can%20be%20with%20your%20family%20and%20friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20the%20proposed%20New%20York%20bill%20could%20impact%20Chick-fil-A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bill%20proposed%20by%20New%20York%20lawmakers%20would%20require%20all%20restaurants%20contracted%20to%20operate%20at%20rest%20areas%20on%20the%20state%20highway%20system%20to%20be%20open%20seven%20days%20a%20week.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnyassembly.gov%2Fleg%2F%3Fdefault_fld%3D%26leg_video%3D%26bn%3DA08336%26term%3D2023%26Summary%3DY%26Actions%3DY%26Memo%3DY%26Text%3DY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegislation%3C%2Fa%3E%20applies%20to%20%26quot%3Bfood%20services%20at%20transportation%20facilities%20and%20rest%20areas%20owned%20and%20operated%20by%20certain%20public%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20text%20submitted%20with%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20bill%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20motorists%20have%20reliable%20access%20to%20food%20while%20traveling%20on%20state%20highways%20by%20requiring%20restaurants%20to%20be%20open%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20there%20is%20nothing%20objectionable%20about%20a%20fast%20food%20restaurant%20closing%20on%20a%20particular%20day%20of%20the%20week%2C%20service%20areas%20dedicated%20to%20travelers%20is%20an%20inappropriate%20location%20for%20such%20a%20restaurant.%20Publicly%20owned%20service%20areas%20should%20use%20their%20space%20to%20maximally%20benefit%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20written%20justification%20for%20the%20bill%20reads.%20%26quot%3BAllowing%20for%20retail%20space%20to%20go%20unused%20one%20seventh%20of%20the%20week%20or%20more%20is%20a%20disservice%20and%20unnecessary%20inconvenience%20to%20travelers%20who%20rely%20on%20these%20service%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasically%2C%20it%20means%20New%20York%20state%20would%20only%20issue%20new%20contracts%20for%20rest%20areas%20to%20restaurants%20that%20will%20be%20open%20seven%20days%20a%20week.%20So%20it's%20true%20that%20the%20bill%20could%20mean%20Chick-fil-A%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20open%20new%20locations%20in%20highway%20rest%20areas%20unless%20the%20location%20agrees%20to%20open%20on%20Sundays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20applies%20to%20all%20restaurants%2C%20Chick-fil-A%20was%20mentioned%20in%20text%20related%20to%20the%20bill.%20The%20Democratic%20lawmaker%20who%20introduced%20the%20bill%2C%20State%20Assemblymember%20Tony%20Simone%2C%20also%20mentioned%20the%20restaurant%20by%20name%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fnew-york-rest-stops-chick-fil-a-17e5a44140f0cb383fa31429bf66184b%5C%22%20targe