causing%20patchiness.%20While%20different%20brushes%20are%20intended%20for%20different%20purposes%2C%20there%20aren't%20technically%20any%20hard%20and%20fast%20rules.%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20to%20find%20what%20works%20for%20you%20and%20invest%20in%20quality%20brushes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20bristle%20softness%20is%20a%20major%20indicator%20of%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20feeling%20luxurious%2C%20the%20softest%20brushes%20will%20also%20help%20your%20makeup%20to%20look%20its%20best.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20they%20are%20natural%20hair%20or%20synthetic%2C%20you%20want%20something%20that%20feels%20soft%20to%20touch%20against%20the%20eyes%20and%20face%20%E2%80%94%20this%20will%20be%20key%20to%20blending%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20makeup%20artist%20and%20Stila%20Global%20Beauty%20Director%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcharlieriddle%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Riddle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BAny%20brush%20that%20is%20more%20coarse%20will%20make%20your%20makeup%20look%20more%20textured%20and%20difficult%20to%20blend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20choosing%20brushes%2C%20it's%20also%20helpful%20to%20consider%20how%20often%20you'll%20use%20them.%20If%20you%20typically%20use%20makeup%20brushes%20daily%20or%20travel%20with%20them%20regularly%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20it%20to%20invest%20in%20high-quality%20ones.%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20look%20for%20quality%20because%20I%20wash%20them%20so%20often%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Los%20Angeles-based%20makeup%20artist%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftarrynfeldman%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETarryn%20Feldman%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20top%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20makeup%20brushes%2C%20according%20to%20makeup%20artists%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20best%20face%20brushes%3Cp%3EThis%20multitasking%20tool%20features%20a%20large%20fluffy%20brush%20on%20one%20end%20and%20a%20smaller%2C%20more%20precise%20brush%20on%20the%20other.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20dual%20ended%20brushes%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Riddle.%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20are%20you%20getting%20two%20for%20one%20but%20this%20is%20great%20for%20buffing%20on%20a%20light%20foundation%20or%20cream%20products.%20I%20love%20to%20apply%20concealer%20or%20highlighter%20with%20the%20smaller%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20treat%20yourself%20to%20one%20luxury%20makeup%20brush%2C%20make%20it%20this%20one.%20%26quot%3BDefinitely%20a%20splurge%20but%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Riddle%20says%20of%20the%20fluffy%20face%20brush.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20so%20soft%20and%20perfect%20for%20applying%20powders.%20Every%20product%20goes%20on%20effortlessly%20with%20this%20brush.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelebrity%20makeup%20artist%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjamiebeaute%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJamie%20Dorman%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommends%20this%20brush%20due%20to%20its%20ultra-soft%20fibers%20that%20allow%20for%20flawless%20foundation%20application.%20%26quot%3BIts%20gentle%20bristles%20make%20for%20a%20glowing%2C%20skin-like%20finish%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20double-sided%20nature%20of%20this%20brush%20makes%20it%20suitable%20for%20both%20liquid%20or%20cream%20blush%20as%20well%20as%20other%20face%20products.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sponge%20end%20stipples%20on%20the%20product%20and%20the%20brush%20end%20can%20blend%20the%20edges%20and%20apply%20a%20powder%20blush%20on%20top%20for%20longevity%2C%26quot%3B%20Dorman%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20highlighter%20fanatic%2C%20this%20brush%20will%20make%20a%20great%20addition%20to%20your%20collection.%20The%20fluffy%20tapered%20end%20is%20ideal%20for%20diffusing%20liquid%20or%20powder%20highlighter%20as%20well%20as%20precise%20powder%20application%2C%20Dorman%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fluffy%20powder