0the%20opinion%20of%20these%20judges%20that%20what%20was%20done%20was%20correct%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20of%20the%20five-judge%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20had%20disappointed%20many%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20accepting%20the%20court's%20judgment%20that%20the%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%20was%20temporary%20in%20nature%20and%20its%20removal%20was%20correct%20in%20terms%20of%20procedure%2C%20many%20political%20leaders%20had%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bstruggle%26quot%3B%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20issue%2C%20which%20he%20insisted%20deserved%20to%20be%20put%20to%20rest%2C%20Justice%20Kaul%2C%20who%20retired%20on%20December%2025%2C%20said%20the%20issues%20which%20came%20before%20the%20bench%20could%20be%20broadly%20divided%20into%20two%20questions%20--%20whether%20the%20Article%20370%20was%20a%20temporary%20provision%20and%20whether%20the%20Centre%20had%20stuck%20to%20the%20correct%20legal%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20%26quot%3Bshell%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bslightly%20different%20procedure%26quot%3B%20used%20to%20assimilate%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20India%20should%20stay%20or%20go%20was%20a%20political%20decision%2C%20Justice%20Kaul%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20decision%20for%20full%20assimilation%20has%20been%20taken%2C%20it%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bcorrect%20legal%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20On%20the%20question%20of%20process%2C%20the%20court%20took%20its%20call%20looking%20at%20the%20ground%20reality%20--%20that%20there%20was%20no%20state%20assembly%20at%20the%20time%20and%20the%20power%20rested%20with%20the%20Centre.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20are%20entitled%20to%20a%20different%20opinion%20of%20it%2C%20so%20what%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20temporary%20position%2C%20all%20five%20judges%20had%20agreed%20it%20was%2C%20going%20by%20the%20incorporation%20and%20the%20chapter%20where%20it%20was%20made.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20he%20felt%20about%20the%20situation%20since%20he%20felt%20the%20pain%20of%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20--%20the%20judge%20is%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20--%20he%20said%20it%20was%20essential%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20something%20wrong%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%20Citing%20the%20South%20African%20model%2C%20based%20not%20on%20retribution%20or%20revenge%20but%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20wrongdoing%20and%20a%20system%20of%20apology%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20what%20people%20need%20to%20move%20on.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2011%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20a%20unanimous%20judgment%2C%20upheld%20the%20Centre's%20decision%20to%20scrap%20the%20provisions%20of%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20had%20granted%20special%20status%20to%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20court%20said%20the%20Centre's%20decision%20to%20bifurcate%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20valid%2C%20it%20also%20directed%20that%20the%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20be%20done%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703788620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6ukfd938_justice-sk-kaul-_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpeople-can-have-a-different-opinion-retired-judge-on-article-370-verdict-4760270%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unanimous%20judgment%20on%20Kashmir%20was%20the%20opinion%20of%20five%20judges%20and%20people%20can%20differ%2C%20Justice%20(Retd)%20SK%20Kaul%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20constitution%20bench%20that%20delivered%20the%20verdict%2C%20told%20NDTV%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22cano