ceremony%20will%20be%20held%20privately%20on%20December%2029.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fpayback-money-and-power-team-to-skip-sbs-drama-awards-in-respect-of-lee-sun-kyun-celebrities-to-pay-tribute-with-a-black-dress-code%2Farticleshow%2F106358306.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20CBSE%20Affiliation%20Fraud%2C%20Manipur%20Probe%20Team%20Checking%20Who%20Signed%20Papers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20three-member%20team%20looking%20into%20how%2025%20schools%20in%20violence-hit%20Manipur%20applied%20for%20CBSE%20affiliation%20without%20the%20state%20government's%20permission%20will%20give%20its%20report%20by%20January%205%2C%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20on%20December%2019%20cancelled%20the%20affiliation%20of%20the%2025%20schools%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20action%20came%20four%20days%20after%20the%20state%20government%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20it%20had%20not%20issued%20the%20no-objection%20certificates%20(NOCs)%20that%20the%20schools%20had%20given%20to%20the%20central%20board%20while%20applying%20for%20affiliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE's%20bylaws%20make%20it%20a%20must%20for%20state%20board%20schools%20to%20bring%20NOCs%20from%20the%20state%20government%20before%20applying%20to%20the%20central%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-member%20team%20is%20checking%20who%20are%20the%20officers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F25-schools-in-manipur-churachandpur-kangpokpi-lose-cbse-affiliation-over-alleged-paperwork-fraud-4705442%5C%22%3Ewho%20issued%20the%20NOCs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20schools%20illegally%2C%20and%20whether%20other%20people%20have%20forged%20the%20signatures%20on%20the%20NOC%20papers%2C%20sources%20said.%20The%20team%20will%20also%20suggest%20what%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20found%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20school%20education%20department%20director%20L%20Nandakumar%20Singh%20is%20leading%20the%20investigation%20team.%20The%20department's%20additional%20director%20(valley)%20Bisheshwar%20Khumukcham%2C%20and%20additional%20director%20(hills)%20Dangmei%20Manglem%20are%20the%20two%20other%20members%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20started%20after%20local%20Congress%20worker%20Lamtinthang%20Haokip%2C%20who%20lost%20the%202022%20assembly%20election%20from%20Saitu%20seat%2C%20on%20December%2014%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%2020%20schools%20in%20Churachandpur%20and%2016%20in%20Kangpokpi%20have%20been%20successfully%20affiliated%20to%20the%20CBSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F2cho9q4_lamtinthang-x_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20of%20the%20education%20board%20from%20state%20to%20central%20in%20the%20two%20hill%20districts%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20soft%20attempt%20at%20formalising%20a%20new%20arrangement%2C%20since%20clashes%20between%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20Meiteis%20began%20on%20May%203.%20The%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20been%20demanding%20what%20they%20call%20a%20%26quot%3Bseparate%20administration%26quot%3B%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Mr%20Haokip's%20social%20media%20post%2C%20Manipur%20Education%20Minister%20Th%20Basanta%20told%20reporters%20the%20state%20government%20has%20not%20given%20NOCs%20to%20any%20school%20since%20May%202020.%20Mr%20Basanta%20then%20met%20the%20Union%20Education%20Ministry%20secretary%20and%20gave%20a%20letter%20explaining%20the%20issue%2C%20following%20which%20the%20CBSE%20cancelled%20the%20affiliations%20of%20the%2025%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20SARAS%204.0%20website%20on%20December%2020%20removed%20the%2025%20schools%20in%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Churachandpur%20from%20its%20list%20of%20affiliated%20schools.%20SARAS%20is%20short%20for%20'School%20Affiliation%20Re-Engineered%20Automation%20System'%20that%20updates%20in%20real-time%20the%20affiliation%20status%20of%20over%2028%2C900%20schools%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20narrowed%20down%20to%20an%20education%20officer%20in%20Kangpokpi%20and%20a%20former%20education%20officer%20in%20Churachandpur%20for%20allegedly%20handing%20out%20NOCs%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20education%20department%20had%20told%20NDTV%20on%20December%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEleven%20of%20the%2025%20schools%20got%20CBSE%20affiliation%20in%20the%20period%20between%20May%202020%20and%20May%202023%2C%20and%2014%20received%20affiliation%20in%20the%20past%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Facm0chgo_cbse-saras_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Churachandpur%2C%20none%20of%20the%20four%20schools%20that%20lost%20CBSE%20affiliation%20had%20working%20phone%20numbers.%20One%20had%20only%20'0000'%20as%20the%20contact%20number.%20Not%20having%20working%20phones%20and%20having%20inconsistent%20details%20such%20as%20the%20phone%20number%20or%20address%20of%20the%20principal%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20of%20a%20relative%20are%20violations%20of%20the%20CBSE's%20bylaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20after%20May%203%20was%20such%20that%20functioning%20under%20the%20state%20board%20was%20becoming%20impossible.%20We%20have%20to%20go%20to%20Imphal%20for%20exam%20coordination%20and%20other%20state%20board%20work.%20How%20would%20that%20be%20possible%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20principal%20of%20a%20Kangpokpi%20school%20freshly%20affiliated%20with%20the%20CBSE%20told%20NDTV%20on%20December%2020%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%2C%20before%20the%20affiliation%20was%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20school%20principal%20in%20Kangpokpi%20said%20they%20have%20followed%20due%20process%20in%20applying%20for%20NOC%2C%20and%20showed%20the%20letters%20they%20have%20written%20to%20the%20education%20department%20seeking%20NOC%20for%20education%20board%20switch.%20Though%20this%20principal%20could%20not%20show%20the%20education%20department's%20response%2C%20he%20showed%20the%20NOC%20they%20have%20received%20from%20the%20zonal%20education%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hill%20district%20school%20principals%20cited%20difficulty%20in%20coordinating%20with%20the%20education%20department%20at%20a%20time%20when%20battle%20lines%20have%20been%20clearly%20drawn%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20ethnicity%20and%20deep%20mistrust.%20All%20the%20principals%20NDTV%20spoke%20to%20in%20Kangpokpi%20requested%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F7sken738_cbse-manipur-affiliation_625x300_19_December_23.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%2C%20however%2C%20has%20indicated%20it%20would%20take%20action%20against%20more%20schools%20including%20withdrawing%20their%20affiliation%20if%20any%20of%20them%20is%20again%20found%20not%20following%20due%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20principals%20are%20not%20thinking%20right.%20What%20are%20they%20implying%3F%20Short-circuit%20adminis