t-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20to%20win%20Test%20matches%2C%20we%20have%20to%20come%20together%20collectively%20and%20we%20didn't%20do%20that.%20Guys%20have%20come%20here%20before%2C%20we%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20and%20everyone%20has%20their%20own%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20batters%20were%20challenged%20and%20we%20didn't%20adapt%20well.%20This%20is%20a%20boundary-scoring%20ground%2C%20we%20saw%20them%20score%20many%20but%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20opposition%20and%20their%20strengths%20as%20well.%20We%20didn't%20bat%20well%20in%20both%20innnings%2C%20that's%20why%20we%20stand%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20skipper%20struggled%20to%20find%20much%20positives%20with%20the%20match%20ending%20inside%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20too%20many%20positives%20to%20finish%20the%20game%20within%20three%20days%2C%20but%20KL%20showed%20what%20we%20need%20to%20do%20on%20this%20sort%20of%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKL%20Rahul%20had%20scored%20a%20century%20in%20the%20first%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20bowlers%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20guys%20haven't%20been%20here%20before%20so%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20too%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImportant%20for%20us%20to%20regroup%2C%20we%20go%20through%20these%20times%20as%20sportsmen%20and%20we%20need%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20Test%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlaying%20his%20last%20international%20series%2C%20Dean%20Elgar%20slammed%20a%20magnificent%20185%20and%20the%20opener%20termed%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%26quot%3B%20knock%20and%20highlighted%20his%20partnerships%20with%20Tony%20de%20Zorzi%20(28)%20and%20Marco%20Jansen%20(84).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPretty%20special%20knock.%20Sometimes%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do%20hasn't%20worked%20out%20as%20plans%2C%20but%20happy%20that%20it%20worked%20today.%20I%20think%20you%20need%20to%2