ders%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Karnataka%20Allege%20Graft%20Within%20Party%3B%20National%20Secy.%20Sacked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F28200750%2FHazra-N-Nadda.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20BJP%20national%20secretary%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20who%20accused%20leaders%20of%20the%20state%20unit%20for%20allegedly%20diverting%20funds%20from%20a%20Gita%20Path%20event%2C%20was%20removed%20from%20his%20central%20post%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20on%20December%2024%2C%20Anupam%20Hazra%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20his%20social%20media%20account%20that%20passes%20for%20the%20Gita%20Path%20program%20at%20the%20Brigade%20Parade%20Grounds%20were%20being%20sold%20by%20party%20leaders%20at%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20head.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20VIP%20passes%20were%20made%20for%20Gita%20Path%20for%20some%20VIP%20people.%20It%20was%20given%20to%20block-level%20leaders%20of%20BJP%20to%20be%20given%20to%20some%20people.%20However%2C%20in%20Birbhum%E2%80%99s%20Nalhati%2C%20these%20cards%20are%20being%20sold%20for%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fbjp-anupam-hazra-bengal-jp-nadda-9085017%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20demanded%20an%20enquiry%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20were%20in%20Kolkata%20to%20review%20preparations%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20Hazra%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20his%20post%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20unit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20the%20instructions%20of%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20National%20President%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20Anupam%20Hazra%20is%20relieved%20from%20the%20post%20of%20national%20secretary.%20This%20should%20be%20followed%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20BJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20Arun%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20Poush%20Mela%20in%20Santiniketan%2C%20Hazra%20set%20up%20a%20booth%2C%20encouraging%20discontented%20BJP%20members%20and%20dissatisfied%20workers%20to%20express%20their%20grievances%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHazra%20has%20had%20run-ins%20with%20the%20party%20leadership%20both%20at%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20professor%20at%20Visva-Bharati%20University%2C%20he%20had%20first%20been%20elected%20in%202014%20from%20the%20Bolpur%20constituency%20on%20a%20TMC%20ticket%2C%20having%20defeated%20the%20CPI(M)%20by%20over%202.5%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20then%20alleged%20being%20disallowed%20from%20taking%20independent%20decisions%20due%20to%20the%20political%20influence%20of%20powerful%20party%20leaders%20from%20his%20region%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20being%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20in%20January%202019%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20got%20a%20ticket%20for%20the%20Jadavpur%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20but%20lost%20to%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Mimi%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202020%2C%20Hazra%20was%20appointed%20as%20national%20secretary%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%2C%20taking%20over%20from%20Rahul%20Sinha%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20unit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20reappointed%20Hazra%20as%20national%20secretary%20for%20a%20second%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20developments%20in%20West%20Bengal%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20turmoil%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Karnataka%20unit%2C%20which%20is%20also%20facing%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20from%20within%2C%20reflecting%20apparent%20infighting%20between%20two%20factions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fbjp-mla-says-yediyurappa-was-involved-in-rs-40000cr-corruption-in-covid-management%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Basangouda%20Patil%20Yatnal%2C%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20accused%20former%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%20of%20acquiring%20face%20masks%20at%20an%20inflated%20rate%2C%20resulting%20in%20irregularities%20totaling%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYatnal%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20involved%20in%20trying%20to%20conceal%20the%20alleged%20scam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKarnataka%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20urged%20Yatnal%20to%20submit%20all%20pertinent%20documents%20to%20the%20Justice%20Nagamohan%20Das%20Commission%2C%20which%20was%20investigating%20allegations%20related%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9840%25%20commission%E2%80%99%20allegations%20made%20by%20contractors%20during%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKarnataka%20BJP%20general%20secretary%20P.%20Rajeev%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20party%20had%20taken%20note%20of%20certain%20recent%20developments%20and%20would%20not%20tolerate%20any%20activities%20that%20cause%20damage%20to%20its%20dignity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%