n%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Taniya%20Roy%3A%20%3Cem%3EFunny%20Boy%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Shyam%20Selvadurai%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20book%20taught%20me%20a%20very%20simple%20thing%3A%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20be%20extremely%20emotional.%20When%20you%E2%80%99re%20a%20child%20and%20no%20adult%20in%20the%20family%20wants%20to%20know%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20going%20through%2C%20you%20deal%20with%20difficult%20emotions%20on%20your%20own.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20always%20manage%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way.%20Be%20true%20to%20yourself%2C%20be%20honest%20with%20yourself%2C%20and%20help%20others%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3A%20%3Cem%3ECrying%20in%20H%20Mart%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Michelle%20Zauner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKorean%20American%20Michelle%20Zauner%2C%20best%20known%20as%20the%20singer%2C%20guitarist%20and%20songwriter%20of%20the%20indie-pop%20band%20Japanese%20Breakfast%2C%20writes%20about%20losing%20her%20mother%20to%20cancer%2C%20battling%20grief%20and%20coming%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20parent%20she%20resented%20for%20most%20of%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZauner%E2%80%99s%20autobiographical%20tale%20is%20sublime%20and%20casts%20the%20narrative%20in%20the%20immigrant%20experience%20of%20many%20Americans%20who%20would%20rather%20invisibilise%20their%20cultural%20difference%20than%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cother%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20tells%20the%20tale%20of%20many%20women%20who%20have%20difficult%20relationships%20with%20their%20mothers%20and%20only%20grow%20to%20appreciate%20them%20when%20they%E2%80%99re%20older%2C%20and%20often%2C%20as%20in%20Zauner%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20when%20they%20are%20about%20to%20lose%20them%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20ultimately%20sees%20Zauner%20come%20into%20herself%2C%20accept%20her%20individuality%2C%20heritage%2C%20culture%20and%20identity%20as%20she%20loses%20the%20person%20who%20made%20her%20%E2%80%9Cdifferent%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20was%20recommended%20to%20me%20by%20a%20friend%20and%20I%20could%20not%20be%20more%20grateful%20as%20it%20brought%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20in%20how%20I%20subsequently%20heard%20Zauner%E2%80%99s%20music%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20being%20a%20longtime%20fan%20of%20Japanese%20Breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Devirupa%20Mitra%3A%20A%20journey%20to%20Ancient%20Egypt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20always%20an%20embarrassment%20of%20riches%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20finding%20good%20overview%20books%20with%20rigorous%20research%20but%20approachable%20writing%20on%20ancient%20history%20in%20the%20western%20world.%20But%20when%20one%20starts%20to%20look%20beyond%20towards%20Ancient%20Egypt%20%E2%80%93%20it%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20digging%2C%20perhaps%20because%20their%20writer-historians%20are%20not%20as%20well%20known.%C2%A0%20Consequently%2C%20the%20discoveries%20I%20made%20and%20enjoyed%20this%20year%20were%20delightful%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20compelling%20starting%20point%20for%20venturing%20into%20Ancient%20Egypt%20is%20biography%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FRamesses-Great-Egypts-Kings-Ancient-ebook%2Fdp%2FB0BZZF24SW%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1%3Fcrid%3D3JTPBJQD2K5SM%26keywords%3Dtoby%2Bwilkinson%2Bramesses%26qid%3D1703586791%26s%3Ddigital-text%26sprefix%3Dtoby%2Bwilkinson%2Bramesses%2Cdigital-text%2C516%26sr%3D1-1%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FRamesses-Great-Egypts-Kings-Ancient-ebook%2Fdp%2FB0BZZF24SW%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1%3Fcrid%3D3JTPBJQD2K5SM%26amp%3Bkeywords%3Dtoby%2Bwilkinson%2Bramesses%26amp%3Bqid%3D1703586791%26amp%3Bs%3Ddigital-text%26amp%3Bsprefix%3Dtoby%2Bwilkinson%2Bramesses%2Cdigital-text%2C516%26amp%3Bsr%3D1-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERamesses%20the%20Great%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Toby%20Wilkinson%3C%2Fa%3E