0pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20The%20oyster%20is%20closed%20and%20is%20kept%20on%20antibiotics%20inside%20a%20smaller%20water%20tank%20for%20two%20to%20three%20days%20and%20then%20shifted%20to%20a%20bigger%20pond.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oyster%20then%20secretes%20nacre%20%5Ba%20form%20of%20calcium%20carbonate%5D%20around%20the%20nucleus.%20The%20pearls%20get%20readied%20to%20be%20harvested%20in%2012%20to%2014%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20shares%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20start%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20for%20beginners%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20identify%20good%20oysters%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20says%20that%20it%20is%20much%20easier%20to%20cultivate%20oysters%20and%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20provided%20you%20cultivate%20good%20quality%20oysters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSource%20good%20quality%20oysters%20to%20get%20A-grade%20quality%20pearls.%20The%20size%20of%20the%20oyster%20should%20be%20between%202.5%20to%203%20inches.%20Its%20outer%20cover%20should%20be%20golden%20in%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20the%20market%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20highlights%20that%20usually%20%E2%80%98designer%20debris%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98irritants%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20Ganesha%2C%20Rama%2C%20Shiva%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%20(holy%20number%20in%20Islam)%2C%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20final%20pearls%20come%20out%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20these%20symbols%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20Sanjay%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20be%20informed%20about%20the%20market%20demand.%20If%20you%20implant%20the%20nucleus%20of%20Ganesh%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20go%20to%20sell%20in%20a%20Ram%20temple%2C%20then%20it%20would%20not%20be%20profitable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3